      eucalgf $p |- E : ( NN0 X. NN0 ) --> ( NN0 X. NN0 ) $=
        ( vm vn cn0 cxp wf wfn cv co wcel wral ffnoprv c2nd cfv cc0 wceq cmo
        cop cif cvv visset opex ifex a1i rgen fnopab2g mpbi wa opelxpi adantr
        eucalgval2 iftrue sylan9eq eleq1d mpbird wn iffalse simpr cn cz zmodcl
        nn0z sylan adantrr wo elnn0 anbi1i pm5.61 bitri sylan2b anassrs
        syl11anc eqeltrd pm2.61dan df-opr syl5eqel rgen2 mpbir2an ) GGHZWBCICWB
